songs.title: Yes Please
songs.lyrics:
(Jump on my pleasure pill? ......... YES PLEASE, HA HA!)

[Verse 1]
I cannot sleep
THERE'S TOO MUCH NOISE IN MY HEEAAD!
I cannot sleep
I WANT IT HEEEERE INSTEEEAAD!

[Chorus 1]
I never thought that this could come to this
I just wanna look at your face in peace now
You will never miss
BUT I CAN'T!

(Ha ha ha!)

[Verse 2]
I cannot keep
THE SHAME THAT'S CLAWED US OUT!
And I will not keep
YOUR SHUT UP, SHUT UP LIIIEES!

[Chorus 2]
I never thought that this could come to this
I just wanna live in bliss, in peace now
You will never miss
BUT I CAN!

(Ha ha ha!)
